 6 ###·Added
 7 -·`list_data`·and·`list_assets`·have·a·new·parameter·`q`·that·can·be·used·the·same·way·the·query·language·is·used·in·the·web·platform
 8 -·Deployment·has·new·methods:·`set_training_data`,·`check_training_data_metrics_status`·and·`disable_training_data_reference`,·that·can·be·used·for·monitoring·and·unsupervised·metrics.
